cast.overview: A vehicle crash in the Pine Barrens leads to a missing teen which raises conspiracy theories about the infamous Jersey Devil legend. On the anniversary of the crash, Sarah Franklin, convinced her cousin Kelsey is alive, goes out to the crash site with Alex, Kelsey's boyfriend, to investigate. Things go downhill quickly as Sarah and Alex uncover what really lurks in the woods.
cast.title: Reed's Point

cast.overview: As Valentine's Day approaches, a high school senior attracts the attention of a new student who may have ulterior motives.
cast.title: The Wrong Valentine
